reviewText: I saw this video once several years  ago. I have been looking for a copy for 30 years. I was one of the actors /stuntman in it. I played slim. I thought it was well done.

As a Julie Strain fan I was incredibly disappointed.  This video features horrible acting, is filmed in video, terrible/ lame jokes, and when anyone  besides buns or guns gets naked it is done in that crappy (must think it's  artful) yellow diffused light so you never really see the girls in color.  Julie and her companion do show their ample cleavage, but that is all.  A  total stinker in my book.  The best part of this video came when the  credits rolled and I knew it was over.  You can't even fast forward through  the bad parts, because that's all there is.
